This paper discusses variance reduction methods in stochastic optimization, which is a common topic in machine learning and optimization research. The use of sparsity operators is also a common technique in these fields. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
